===Noun===
{{en-noun|head=[[event]] [[horizon]]}}

# {{context|astrophysics|lang=en}} The [[gravitational]] [[sphere]] of a [[black hole]] within which the [[escape velocity]] is greater than the [[speed of light]].
# {{context|by extension|lang=en}} A point of no return.

